IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TRIANGLE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  ROWS            PIC 9.
01  I                PIC 9.
01  J                PIC 9.
01  K                PIC 9.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROGRAM.
    DISPLAY "Enter the number of rows: ".
    ACCEPT ROWS.

    PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > ROWS
        PERFORM VARYING J FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL J > ROWS - I
            DISPLAY " " WITH NO ADVANCING
        END-PERFORM
        PERFORM VARYING K FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL K > I
            DISPLAY "* " WITH NO ADVANCING
        END-PERFORM
        DISPLAY ""
    END-PERFORM

    STOP RUN.